name: Cell Machine Z
description:
This is a Mod for the game Cell Machine Made and Developed by Sam Hogan!

The Core Scripts are from the Mystic Mod Source Code!

Extra Cells!

Super Mover! -- Double the Speed of a regular Mover Cell!

Bomb Cell! -- Destroys any cell that touches it! (Obstructs your goal, Not an enemy, an obstacle!)

More Soon!
